what is the problem with turkey ? 
on december 16 , orhan pamuk , one of turkey 's most famous writers , will face a court in istanbul . it must respond to the charge of " insulting the national identity " to be voted in favour of an open discussion of the turkish genocide of 1,5 million armenians in 1915 and 1916 . 
