in his classic defense of freedom of expression , freedom , john stuart mill argued that the most important reason for freedom of expression is to promote competition between the widest possible range of ideas , and that unfettered debate is the best way to test them . 
protecting the ideas of criticism , the government turns them into dogma rigid and no life , that they are true or not . 
if we agree with mill , then a single example of gates corresponds to the category of expression that should be protected . 
recipes for making nuclear bombs are techniques , not ideas . 
the pornography is not the expression of ideas . 
