you never know what pathogen will emerge in the system . 
no later than last year came on the island of the meeting the chikungunya virus , which , like the west nile virus , is transmitted by an insect in the blood . 
it must be constantly vigilant , " continues the dre décary before highlighting that in addition to a supply security , héma-québec must also provide an adequate supply . 
